reviewText:
The BEST Assassin's Creed game in the series.
Based on 51 hours gameplay and 92% Sync.

Pro:
- Story-line in both time lines with plenty of the details;
- the driven character who has tired of the creed's" ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥t seeing only chaos and ruins with it;
- Playing as a Templar;
- Well designed missions and the logical requirement for the 100% Sync;
- the graphic looks like stuck in between AC3 and AC4

